{"tid":755483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】烏克蘭女拍半裸寫真　還獲邀參與色情片演出","createTime":"2018-07-25T08:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T09:01:43.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1200,"dislike":243,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"756a26c79124994541989ddb2b18b3df729c305e","tid":755483,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭女拍半裸寫真集，還獲得了色情片的邀約。<br />\n<br />\n據《sobkor》報導，烏克蘭70歲女子艾蓮娜(Елена Волк)，15年前，陪伴她25年的丈夫身亡後，讓她的人生觀有了重大改變，艾蓮娜說「我不會說70歲是最棒的年齡，但是我現在的確是達到了人生最成功、幸福的巔峰，還感覺到了性慾的高峰期」。<br />\n<br />\n艾蓮娜拍攝了半裸寫真後，還獲邀參與色情片的演出，她說最近的確收到跟一名年輕人拍色情片的邀約，因為近來成年女性跟小鮮肉的題材相當受歡迎，而艾蓮娜也坦承說，她目前沒有男朋友。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180725/640_1d612f3213052cab936da36e78519196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180725%2F640_1d612f3213052cab936da36e78519196.jpg&h=ed238d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180725/640_61115bc889a01694ffb1cdc9b190a4f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180725%2F640_61115bc889a01694ffb1cdc9b190a4f0.jpg&h=6ef56835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180725/640_bc28929f056a9204fd64acc7ea75135a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180725%2F640_bc28929f056a9204fd64acc7ea75135a.jpg&h=18b21383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180725/640_b8a53ff3324bcd448311a4e1dac6876e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180725%2F640_b8a53ff3324bcd448311a4e1dac6876e.jpg&h=369b3d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180725/640_4afc7c595cfda9db518c6d10c86013ea.jpg\" dat